name: The Armadillo and his companion
description:
Print of an original illustration drawn in ink then digitally colored.

Artwork is printed on an 8.5" x 11 archival fine art card stock using archival pigment ink.

name: In cahoots with the Owls
description:
Mr. Owl and his two friends Oomp and Oont. No one really knows what they are up to it would not be a far stretch of the imagination to presume it could be some kind of trouble. Fantastic modern green color with a touch of black and beige. 

This is a print of an original hand drawn Ink drawing by Katie that is digitally colored. 

Actual print measures measures 8.5 x 11 inches and is printed on archival fine art card stock using archival pigment ink.

Each print signed on the back. Shipped flat in a protective sleeve in a bend-proof mailer.

Thank you for stopping by our little store and please feel free to send us any questions or comments.
